channel.title: Project Velox
channel.description:
[center]Hello MoparScape, this is my new project called Project Velox. I'm looking to build up a new developing team for the Upcoming Server that I would like to release and host. I am not sure what base we would you i will let the server coders talk about this amongst them selves.Post below if you are interested. We will be in need for a Web Developer, GFX Team, and one or two other developing partner who will like to code. I will be hosting the server and will attempt to give ideas to the server/client coders. Server Developers: Client Developers Web Developer: Open Spot GFX Team: [ul][li]Open Spot Open Spot Open Spot Open Spot[/li] [li][/li][/ul] Server Goals: Have a stable and enjoyable server Create a great forums Community Provide People with a place were they can have a good time. Maintain a good player average
How old are you? Name? How long have you been Programming? What are you applying for? Why should you be in development team? Why would you like to be part of the team? Any other information you wish can be added here.
[/center]
